## Processing new program files

| Artifact | How it gets processed |
|----------|------------------------|
| **`docs/*_SSOT.md`** | Git merge authority; wiki **ingest** + **index rebuild**; frontmatter **`type: page`** when `doc_type: ssot` |
| **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** | Always-apply / globs load in IDE; **export** â†’ **`config/cursor-program/rules/`**; CI pack parity |
| **`config/cursor-program/templates/*`** | Copied/seeded into consumers as **AGENTS.md** / CLAUDE adapter â€” not auto-applied until install/seed |
| **`.cursor/ai-gateway.json`** | Pack mirror **`ai-gateway.cursor.json`**; UI Models still need restore after upgrades |
| **`.cursor/hooks.json`** | Reference in pack only; live hooks need gate binary on this repo |

